{
  "stem": "14463.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I said to my uncle, let's get off the train in here-- the bus or whatever-- the truck in here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because we're going by-- somewhere by truck, somewhere by train, you know, wherever we could.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And let's stay here, I said, for three, four weeks, catch our breath, get our strength up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we'll go down to Tashkent, which is another 600 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we got off in Kyzylorda.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Quite.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a quite large city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is-- it is about 250,000 people, I would say.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's-- it is populated by [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They are [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're not [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Kazakhis, ?] Kazakh.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They have got eyes like that, yellow face-- yellow skin, very aristocratic, you know, tall people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And with-- you know, what hit me, you know, the first time when I saw them-- they were wearing heavy clothes in summer, you know, with big hats, you know, and heavy clothes in summer.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, why?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Against the sun?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were warm-- they were cooler under the-- hot-- on the warm clothes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were just the opposite, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On top of it, it had the largest-- absolutely the largest rice factory in the whole of Russia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was so large.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had all American machinery, which was bought before the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were so large that apparently, this factory was feeding 10% of the Russian army in rice.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you can imagine the scope of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, a long time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stayed there-- then of course, we did not go any more to Tashkent.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we were able somehow to establish ourselves in there, you know, put our roots in there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we gave up the idea of going to Tashkent.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
